We may share your personal data within and outsides of your country of residence subject to this Privacy Policy. The data protection laws of the jurisdcitions to which your personal data may be transferred might not be as comprehensive as those in your country.
For European Economic Area (EEA) and UK Residents Only
When we transfer your personal data from within the EEA or UK to outside the EEA or UK, we will ensure that it is protected in a manner that is consistent with how your personal data is protected by us in the EEA / UK and an adequate level of protection will be ensured, through one of the following mechanisms:
